{position:relative;top:-20px;width:200px;overflow:hidden;} a:link, a:visited {color:#999;font-weight:bolder;} a:hover, a:active {color:#fff;font-style:italic;} h3 {font-size:14px} h1 {font-size:24px} h2 {font-size:18px} /* Header */ #fw-head {background: #000 url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblacklogo.png) no-repeat top right;height:200px;position:relative;top:0;left:0;width:1000px} #fw-head h1,h2{margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;width:1000px;margin-top:15px} #fw-title {position: absolute; top:20px;font-style:italic;text-align:center} #fw-title a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;text-transform:capitalize} #fw-smalltitle {position: absolute;top:70px;color:#979797;font-style:italic;text-align:center;color:#000} #logo-div {height:200px;} .fw-title {text-transform:capitalize;background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/SleekBlackMainTitle.png) no-repeat center top;height:122px;color:#000;text-align:center;line-height:125px;z-index:1;position:relative;top:-20px;width:750px;margin:20px auto} .fw-logo {margin: 0 auto;background-position:top left;background-repeat:no-repeat;} /* Navigation */ #fw-nav-menu a:hover, a:active, a:link, a:visited {font-style:normal} #fw-nav-menu {width:1000px;position:relative;top:-15px} #fw-nav-menu ul {list-style: none;text-align:center;} #fw-nav-menu li {height:52px;width:164px;text-align:center;background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblack.jpg) no-repeat;margin-left:-4px;display:-moz-inline-stack;display:inline-block;zoom:1;*display:inline;} #fw-nav-menu li:hover {background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblackmo.jpg) no-repeat center;} .fw-current-nav-link {background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblackcurrent.jpg)no-repeat;display:block;height:52px;width:164px;} .fw-current-nav-link:hover {background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblackmo.jpg)} a.section {color:#fff;line-height:33px;font-weight:bold;text-decoration: none;} /* Content */ .hasSidebar #fw-mainColumn {float:left;width:750px} .fw-text {width:690px;margin:0 auto;color:#ddd;padding:130px 30px 50px 30px;background:url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblackbg.jpg) repeat-y;margin-top:-160px;z-index:0;position:relative;} .fw-paragraphbottom {background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblackpbottom.png) no-repeat center;height:73px;width:750px;position:relative;margin:0 auto;margin-top:-50px;} h3.fw-title span {padding-left:60px;padding-right:40px;color:#bbb;} .fw-paragraph {padding-bottom:30px} /* --Sidebar-- */ #fw-sidebar {display:none;border:1px solid #000;width:200px;} .hasSidebar #fw-sidebar {display:block;float:right;} #fw-sidebar .fw-title {background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblackmaintitlesb.png) no-repeat center;height:96px;line-height:53px;width:200px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;top:0;} #fw-sidebar .fw-paragraph {background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblackbgsb.jpg) repeat-y;padding-bottom:0px} #fw-sidebar .fw-paragraphbottom {background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblackpbottomsb.png) no-repeat center;height:136px;width:200px;margin-top:0px;} #fw-sidebar .fw-text {background: transparent;color:#ddd;width:170px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:15px;padding-bottom:0px;margin-top:-25px;text-align:center;} /* Footer */ #fw-footer {background: url(http://snedekerdesignz.webs.com/templates/sleekblack/sleekblackfooter.png) no-repeat center;height:119px;width:1000px;text-align:center;margin:0 auto;} .fw-footertext {font-weight:bolder;line-height:70px;} /* Clears */ .clears {clear: both;}
